== Play DVD files (VOB+IFO) from hard drive<br>  ==

Use '''Media -&gt; Open Disc''', and instead of '''DVD drive''', point the location to correct folder by using either '''Browse''' button or customize field . 



For example:<br> 
<pre>''dvd://"c:\movies\BLOOD DIAMOND\VIDEO_TS"''
</pre> 
